ABOUT :
HFTirc.
   * Hacker Feeding Themselves irc

A highly configurable and simple irc client.

LICENSE : BSD

REQUIREMENT :
  - cmake
  - ncurses
  - libncurses5
  - libncurses5-dev (debian based distro)
  - libncursesw5
  - libncuresw5-dev (debian based distro)

OS :
  - GNU/Linux : Supported.
  - FreeBSD/NetBSD : Supported.

INSTALL :
cd HFTirc
cmake .
make
sudo make install

DISTROS :
  - HFTirc is available with AUR in ArchLinux (http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=45899)
